      • newOutputStream

        public static CustomZipOutputStream newOutputStream(Path zipFile)
                                             throws IOException
        Create a new CustomZipOutputStream that outputs to the given zipFile. Note that the parent directory of the zipFile must exist already. The returned stream will throw an exception should duplicate entries be added.
        Parameters:
        zipFile - The file to write to.
        Throws:
        IOException
